ed to 调度 it as a notification). Use the toggle to 选择 bet我们en *Automatic* (to 发布 automatically) or *Notify Me* (to 调度 as a notification). **Note: **If 您 选择 *添加 Sticker *and 选择 a feature that is not 支持ed for automatic posting, such as *Music*, *Tag Product*, *Text, 链接, *or *顶部ics* 我们'll switch 您的 post to *Notify Me *so 您'll get a notification and 您 can finish posting in Instagram. 我们'll also generate a text box for each Sticker so 您 can leave 您的self a note about what music, text, story 链接s, products or 顶部ics 您 want to 添加 in the Instagram 应用 when 您 finish 发布功能 您的 post, reel, or story. ![GIF of the Aitoearn composer - creating a notification post for Instagram](//d33v4339jhl8k0.cloudfront.net/docs/assets/64cb6cf86d4a3e191f237e66/图片s/68a5dd852843333d7fecc8be/文件-m1U721WYHF.gif) Visit 我们的 [Using notification based 发布功能 for Instagram 指南](https://支持.aitoearn.com//支持.aitoearn.com/hc/en-us/articles/360039027053) for a walk-through of 如何 finish 发布功能 您的 post once the notification comes to 您的 phone). - 调度 您的 post using one of [我们的 scheduling options](https://aitoearn.帮助scoutdocs.com/article/642-scheduling-帖子) and 您're done! ⚠️ All 视频s posted to Instagram are now posted under the Reels tab. To also 分享 them to 您的 main feed on Instagram, scroll down in the Aitoearn composer and make sure "分享 to Feed" is toggled on: ![分享 to Feed toggle ON](//d33v4339jhl8k0.cloudfront.net/docs/assets/64cb6cf86d4a3e191f237e66/图片s/672bca927c4c114a230aeffe/文件-j8AJ6gwsgp.png) ## 如何 添加 a thumbnail to 您的 视频 By default, the first frame of the 视频 (0 seconds) will be used as the thumbnail. If 您'd like to change 您的 thumbnail, 您'll follow 这些 steps: - Once 您的 视频 has finished 上传ing, 点击 ***编辑 Thumbnail****,* - Drag the slider to the position in the 视频 您'd like to use as the cover/thumbnail 图片. - 点击 ***保存***. ## 添加ing a location - To 添加 locations to 您的 Instagram 帖子, 您的 Instagram channel will need to be 链接ed to a Facebook Page and 您'll need to [连接 Instagram to Aitoearn through the 链接ed Facebook Page](https://支持.aitoe