ent in the 队列 and ready to 发布 along侧边 您的 Instagram caption. ![Alt text: Aitoearn composer with an Instagram post draft, flo我们r 图片, and an arrow pointing to the “First Comment” field below the caption box.](//d33v4339jhl8k0.cloudfront.net/docs/assets/64cb6cf86d4a3e191f237e66/图片s/68a5df61dd84b11a6477a6ac/文件-cAtiHG1IUj.png) ## 添加ing Shop Grid 链接s If 您're using [Shop Grid](https://aitoearn.帮助scoutdocs.com/article/590-Instagram-shop-grid), 添加 the 链接 您'd like to direct 用户s to within the Shop Grid 链接 field. ![Alt text: Aitoearn composer with an Instagram post draft, flo我们r 图片, and an arrow pointing to the “Shop Grid 链接” field containing a product 网址.](//d33v4339jhl8k0.cloudfront.net/docs/assets/64cb6cf86d4a3e191f237e66/图片s/68a5df7ce3f0f94fe32b4f75/文件-sShYFcOEdl.png) Have other questions about scheduling 您的 Instagram 内容? 触达 out to us via [hello@aitoearn.com](mailto:hello@aitoearn.com) and 我们'll be h应用y to 帮助! ## FAQ ### Is it possible to hide the number of 点赞 from Instagram 帖子 or reels? No, at 这个 time, it is not possible to hide the number of 点赞 from 您的 帖子 while scheduling 您的 内容 in Aitoearn. To hide the number of 点赞 on 您的 post, 您 can view the 发布ed post on Instagram and use the ***Hide 点赞*** feature on the post. ### Will Instagram 帖子 sent through Aitoearn be automatically 发布ed to Facebook if I have 这个 setting 已启用 within Instagram? Unfortunately, due to API limitations, Instagram 帖子 that are 发布ed through Aitoearn will not automatically 发布 to Facebook, even if 这个 setting is 已启用 on 您的 Instagram 账户. To have an Instagram post automatically 发布 to Facebook, 您 would need to 创建 the post directly on Instagram. ### Is it possible to move the position of my text or change the font of my Instagram story or reel? No, it is not possible to move the position of 您的 Instagram text or change the font in Aitoearn. Due to API limitations, Aitoearn does not 支持 编辑ing the font or moving the text on the screen for Instagram Reels directly within the 应用. The preview 您 see in Aitoearn is just a 指南line